    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable choice for those seeking a functional daily driver. Mechanically, the engine and transmission are in solid working order, providing a steady performance on the road. However, the exterior shows clear signs of its history, including several noticeable scratches, minor dings, and some fading of the paint. The interior also exhibits moderate wear on the upholstery, though it remains clean and comfortable. This is a practical option for anyone prioritizing utility and reliability over a flawless appearance.",
