    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable ride that\u2019s ready for your daily commute? This vehicle is in fair condition and offers a solid, honest performance that you can count on! It shows some expected signs of use and character, but it remains a practical and reliable choice for anyone seeking a budget-friendly, functional car. Come see how this sturdy vehicle can fit into your life today!",
      "price": 20000.0,
