    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine starts reliably and delivers smooth performance on both city streets and highways. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, though you might notice some minor wear on the driver's seat and a few light scratches on the exterior paint consistent with regular use. All major systems, including the air conditioning and electronics, are fully functional. This is an excellent choice for someone looking for a dependable vehicle that is ready to drive immediately without needing major repairs.",
